{"name": "Kardashians and Memes 1", "description": "The Kardashians converted famous for being famous into massively successful brands and businesses. What started as reflexive became actualized over time. 

The Kardashians are a great analog reference for what memes will do over the coming decade. Memes will be created and proliferated in a completely reflexive fashion, and then over time progressively convert that capital into projects of their choice. 

Meme with intention, because they will find their way into existence.
